meta {
  name: Assign the fulfillment error status to a WebAuthn preregistration factor
  type: http
  seq: 7
}

post {
  url: {{orgUrl}}/webauthn-registration/api/v1/users/{{userId}}/enrollments/{{authenticatorEnrollmentId}}/mark-error
  body: none
  auth: none
}

headers {
  Accept: application/json
  Authorization: SSWS {{apiKey}}
}

docs {
Assigns the fulfillment error status to a WebAuthn preregistration factor for a user. The `/mark-error` path indicates that the specific `FULFILLMENT_ERRORED` AuthFactor status is set on the enrollment.

**Responses:**
- `204`: No Content
- `403`: 
- `404`: 
- `429`:
}
